description: Conflicts during insertions into exchange trees on n nodes.
links: Markus E. Nebel, Digital Search Trees with Keys of Variable Length, R.A.I.R.O. Theoretical Informatics and Applications 30 (6), 1996, 507 - 520 (see (3) on p. 6).

prog: (PARI) b(n) = if (n == 0, 0, if (n == 1, 0, b(n\2) + b((n-1)\2) + (n-1)/n));lista(nn) = {for(n=0, nn, print1(n!*b(n), ", "););} \\ _Michel Marcus_, Aug 13 2013
